description:
Doesn't hurt to work
together sometimes,
I guess. I'll lend you
a hand, too.

Here you can work together with
others and engage in battle.
I am certain you will play
a very active role, my lord.

This is a Co-op Battle
where you play together
with lots of people!
Good luck! ☆
Think carefully\nwhen spending Jewels.\nDon't waste them!

My lord, you can purchase
valuable items using Jewels.
However, you must be
careful not to overspend.
Jewels can be exchanged\nfor delicious fo—\nI mean, valuable items!

You can receive rewards
when you achieve
certain goals!
Good luck! ♪

Looks like it's full of
memories. We've been
through a lot, but it doesn't
hurt to look back sometimes.

Here we can look back
again and again...
on our happy days
together! ♪

You can relive your memories
with all the girls in your life!
Whoop, whoop! ♪
Way to go, Mr. Popular! ☆

You can also receive
items by clearing
quests.
Let's take all we can!

In this quest, you can earn
items required for Training.
I will become stronger
for you, my lord.

You'll receive some nice items
for clearing this quest!
Collect as many as you
can and get super strong!

My lord, let us prepare
for our journey.
It will make for an even
more fulfilling adventure.

Looks like you can join
a Clan.
Why not give it a try?
Could be a lot of fun! ♪

You can join a Clan here.
There are so many
wonderful Clans,
it is difficult to choose.

Want to join a Clan?
It's a lot more fun
going on adventures
as a team!

Here you can look back
at the activities of
friends who participated
in Clan Battles.

Looks like you can
save Battle Records
of your favorite
practice runs.

My lord, your activities
in this Clan Battle have
been recorded. You can now
review them for future battles.

You can go over your
Battle Record for this
Clan Battle!
Let me have a look too!

Hello there!
In this section, you can choose
new music to play on your home
screen or in the guildhouse!

If you're looking to change the
BGM or buy new tracks, you've
come to the right place! We have
a wide selection available!

You can choose all sorts of tracks
to play on your home screen or in
the guildhouse! Why don't you
show me some of your favorites?

This is where you can change
your background music settings!
What kind of track are you after?
Haha, I can't wait to hear it!

This is where you can purchase
new music tracks to use!
You can listen to a sample first,
so feel free to take your time.

Always a pleasure to see you!
Welcome to the music store.
There are so many lovely tracks,
it can be hard to choose, can't it?

Looks like the items found here
are useful for crafting Unique
Equipment. Once you've got
enough, let's try it out ourselves!

It seems these quests may yield
some rather rare resources.
We can use them to craft
Unique Equipment, my lord.

If we collect enough items here,
we might be able to make some
Unique Equipment! This is our
chance to get even stronger!
How could a chocolate cake\nthat you helped create\nbe anything other than delicious?

There must be some mistake.
My love would never produce
anything less than perfect.
Let's try again, shall we?
To think you would help me\ncreate the very cake I was baking\nfor your sake... Teehee.

There's nothing for you to be
ashamed of. I'll be happy to teach
you all the necessary techniques,
no matter how long it may take...

You don't think you were quite on
form today? Ah, but I would eat
anything that was made by your
hands, my love... Teehee.

Any cake that you make is
a priceless treasure to me.
If anyone disrespects it,
I will swiftly end their lives.

Oh, what a wonderful creation
you have brought into the world!
Finally, a chocolate cake that is
truly worthy of my beloved!

Now that we have made this cake
together, you are fully ensnared
in my charms... Let me whisk you
away to a world of sweetness.

I must savor every last morsel
of this symbol of your passion.
The first of many fruits
our love will bear... Teehee.

This is the finest chocolate cake
the world has ever seen.
After all, it is the one that you
put your heart and soul into.

Aw, are you disappointed by
how it turned out? Don't worry,
I'm just happy you did your best.
Your big sis is here for you!
Hmm, I think you might have let\nyour nerves get the better of you.\nLet's try again, shall we?

What a good little brother,
helping your big sis with her
baking! Oh, but no sneaking any
bites yet, you hear?
Ooh, look! The cake has turned\na perfect golden brown!\nYou're so good at this!

It's all right! Don't look so down.
The cake may look a little...
unique, but I'm sure it tastes
perfectly delicious!
This cake is almost as cute\nas my little bro!\nOh, I can't wait to eat it all up!

What's this? I think you've got
chocolate on your fingers there.
Here, let your big sis lick them
nice and clean! Mmmm~!

I think we did a pretty good job!
But I'm sure this isn't the best
my little bro is capable of!
Your big sis always knows!

Wow, this looks super delicious!
You were such a good helper,
it felt as though the cake just
came together like magic!
Aaahhh, a chocolate cake full of\nmy little bro's hard work!\nNo wonder it looks so delicious!

These areas are pretty mystical.
We should be able to find some
great treasure here, but we could
also get hurt if we're not careful.

The ruins ahead seem to be
ancient places of worship.
We should steel ourselves if we
are to seek the treasures within.

Looks like we're heading into
sacred territory, huh?
I can't wait to see what crazy
treasures we'll find here!

Looks like the items we find here
will help us unlock our true
potential! Come on, let's get
stronger than ever before!

This place conceals resources
that will allow us to tap into our
hidden potential. My lord, where
should we begin our search?

Apparently there are items here
that'll let us unlock our own
hidden strength! Where do you
think we should start looking?!

Welcome!
The Guild Association is here
to support you in all your
social endeavors!

I'm your Guild Association
representative, and this is where
you can keep track of all the
friends you've made!

These are all the friends
you've made so far.
I hope you'll support one another
in your adventures!
Select a friend from the list\nto view their profile in detail!

This is where you can
manage your friend list.
I hope you'll meet plenty
of wonderful new people!
You can send friend requests\nor accept those you've received.\nIsn't it wonderful to get along?

Test your strength against
your friends' best parties!
Isn't it wonderful to spur
one another to new heights?

Select the party you'd like
to try facing in battle!
I can't wait to see which
strategy comes out on top!

We've prepared some special
missions to support our
up-and-coming rookies!
Why don't you give them a try?

There's a time-limited campaign
in progress right now!
Don't forget to complete
as many missions as you can!

Try helping out beginner players
by adding them as friends!
Your good deeds might earn you
some shiny rewards!

There's a time-limited campaign
in progress right now!
Don't forget to complete
as many missions as you can!
Thank you for participating!\nAny rewards you haven't claimed\nare still available to collect!

This is the right place to pick up
any rewards you haven't claimed!
Don't forget to collect them
while they're still available!
